name: 李老师不是你老师
content:
Follow-up of the gymnasium collapse in Huanan County, Jiamusi
The local government wanted to threaten the mother of the deceased child with her relative’s job
The mother yelled on the spot: I don’t want my job anymore, I am divorcing the father of the child now, and I will break off relations with the uncle of the child tomorrow, I must do it to the end, you want to pressure me, it won’t work! The Huanan County government is not human!
I have thought of everything for my child, but now I am holding a funeral for my child!

On November 9, a primary school cafeteria in Huaihua City, Hunan Province, was suspected of having white-haired rat heads. This may be the third case of rat heads being found in school cafeterias in the country in recent times.
The school said that the school wanted to improve the food for the students that day, so one of the dishes was spicy diced rabbit, and the parents may have mistaken the rabbit head for a rat head.
